  "title": "More efficient breeding of drought resistant groundnut in India and Australia",
  "abstract": "This article considers breeding programmes aimed at the production of drought resistant genotypes during the 1990s up to 2001. Cost benefit analyses were conducted to compare indirect selection methods with conventional yield selection approaches.",
